                  <p><strong>电池技术：</strong>PERC单晶硅电池</p>
                  <p><strong>电气架构：</strong>20.3V/7.4A，12V系统优化</p>
                  <p><strong>适用场景：</strong>常规曲面，预算优先项目</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-blue-200/50 rounded text-xs">
                  <strong>建议弯曲半径：</strong>&gt;500mm
