              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-emerald-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <i class="fas fa-ribbon text-emerald-600 text-2xl mr-3"></i>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">全柔性版 SO</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                  <p><strong>结构特点：</strong>最大30°弯曲角度</p>
                  <p><strong>电池技术：</strong>SunPower Maxeon Gen III</p>
                  <p><strong>电气架构：</strong>25.52V/5.88A，高压低电流</p>
                  <p><strong>智能旁路：</strong>细粒度遮挡保护</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-emerald-200/50 rounded text-xs">
                  <strong>建议弯曲半径：</strong>200-300mm
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- PRO Version -->
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  <i class="fas fa-crown text-purple-600 text-2xl mr-3"></i>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">增强版 PRO</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                  <p><strong>结构特点：</strong>200°弧度适应能力</p>
                  <p><strong>美学设计：</strong>全黑外观选项</p>
                  <p><strong>耐候强化：</strong>增厚ETFE膜</p>
                  <p><strong>目标市场：</strong>高端定制项目</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-purple-200/50 rounded text-xs">
                  <strong>建议弯曲半径：</strong>~200mm（极端曲面）
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 data-highlight">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">技术升级路径</h4>
              <p class="mb-0">
                从标准版到SO/PRO版的技术升级体现在电池技术（PERC→IBC）、弯曲能力（15°→30°→200°）、
                以及智能化程度（传统旁路→智能旁路设计）的全面提升
                <a href="https://www.nauticexpo.cn/prod/shenzhen-ahony-power-co-ltd/product-198811-603227.html" class="citation">[246]</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
